This package contains classes that represent the data model of the Material Exchange Format (MXF) as defined by the SMPTE st0377-1:2011 specification.

    IMFConstraints

Package com.netflix.imflibrary Description

This package contains classes that represent the data model of the Material Exchange Format (MXF) as defined by the SMPTE st0377-1:2011 specification. It also contains classes that are used to represent the metadata of an MXF essence in an Interoperable Master Format (IMF) compliant Composition Playlist as defined by the SMPTE st2067-3:2013 specification and constrained by the SMPTE IMF-Core Constraints SMPTE st2067-2:2013.
Since:
1.0
